OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud with bright and
OL,6,Fsunny spells. A few showers around
OL,7,Fthrough the day, which may be heavy,
OL,8,Fbut still plenty of long dry spells.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FShowers mostly dying out this
OL,11,Fevening with late bright or sunny
OL,12,Fspells. Overnight will be dry with
OL,13,Fclear spells before cloud and patchy
OL,14,Frain spreads northwards around dawn.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FA cloudy morning with a few
OL,17,Fspots of rain. Outbreaks of mostly
OL,18,Flight and patchy rain through the
OL,19,Fafternoon but heavier downpours
OL,20,Fpossible in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
