OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells and some heavy showers
OL,7,FTuesday. Bright spells and showers at
OL,8,Ffirst Wednesday, heavy rain later.
OL,9,FMostly cloudy with heavy showers on
OL,10,FThursday. Breezy Wednesday and
OL,11,FThursday.
